            <title>[CASSANDRA-9366] make Functions.declared thread-safe</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9366</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Functions.declared&lt;/tt&gt; is an &lt;tt&gt;ArrayListMultimap&lt;/tt&gt;, which is not thread safe.&lt;br/&gt;
This wasn&apos;t a problem before UDFs. But with UDFs there can be concurrent reads &amp;amp; writes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Need to make it thread safe.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
